com.altcodelabs.methodtrace.analyser

Class TraceManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.altcodelabs.methodtrace.analyser.TraceManager

  • public class TraceManager
extends Object
    Used to handle the traces in the workspace. It primarily uses SQLITE databases to store the traces and perform operations on it.
